name: GOrealler Logo Sweatshirt
description:
Featuring the angery GOrilla face from our logo in white vinyl print on an all black sweatshirt, this piece sums up GOrealler clothing to a T. BOLD and STRONG with a lot of ATTITUDE! Finished off with our motto, "GOrealler, Regret Nothing!"

Made from 100% cotton this sweatshirt is not only stylish but top quality and made to last. These sweatshirt are a fitted cut but open request for the larger sizes (XXL and over) we can source a loser fitting garment.

Washing / Care instructions:
Wash inside out.
Wash with like colours.
Do not iron print.
Do not dry clean.
Wash on a cool wash, we suggest 30 degrees.
Do not bleach.
Following these instructions will ensure the longevity of your garment.

name: Heart Beats
description:
The Heart Beat is a gold plated necklace with a heart shaped speaker pendant. It's inspired by music for music lovers that believe their heart beats to the sound of music! 

Each Heart Beat Necklace has space on the back for a personal engraved message at the extra cost of £5. To have your Heart beat engrave simply select engraved from the drop down menu below. Then leave the message you would like engraved on the back of your heart beat in the shipping details section of the checkout and we'll contact you iimmediately to confirm everything.

Further details:
Heart beat necklaces are gold plated and not solid gold.
each chains is 85m long. chain can be made shorter on request.
The pendant is 5cm wide and 5cm heigh.
